Yeah, it's all debt.

00:22:23.233 --> 00:22:24.867
Everything's debt...

00:22:24.867 --> 00:22:28.067
but my pride's still intact.

00:22:28.067 --> 00:22:31.612
Strong and sturdy!

00:22:31.612 --> 00:22:33.367
If you're scared...

00:22:34.967 --> 00:22:37.133
