01:00:01.267 --> 01:00:02.787
[Hakodate Travel Itinerary]
When pushed to the extreme,

01:00:02.787 --> 01:00:05.667
the choices you make
are ones you don't even realize.

01:00:05.667 --> 01:00:09.033
I think the person you met is the one.

01:00:09.033 --> 01:00:14.400
I couldn't bring myself to say
that she lived by stealing.

01:00:15.367 --> 01:00:18.600
Do you happen to know this person?

01:00:18.600 --> 01:00:21.367
Are you looking for Haruko?

01:00:21.367 --> 01:00:25.333
So, it's the season of storms for everyone.

01:00:26.133 --> 01:00:27.667
Maybe he has been waiting.

01:00:27.667 --> 01:00:30.067
He found the waiting so hard

01:00:30.067 --> 01:00:32.700
that he probably tried to distract
himself with something

01:00:32.700 --> 01:00:34.400
while waiting for her.

01:00:37.867 --> 01:00:39.667
Ms. Haruko.

01:00:39.667 --> 01:00:43.900
Don't you even feel sorry for me?